Flow builder : can't do sending an outbound message without code or invoking a process.
Variable resouce in Flow : holds mutliple field values for mutliple records ; holds values that can be changed any point in the flow.
Record variable : to store multiple field values related to a single ecord in flow designer.
Flows can be launched using user interactions custom button, cutom link or auto launch with process builders.

Read only fields like formula and autonumber can' be used in workflows.

When "Re Evaluate workflow" is checked all the workflows on the associated object whose criteria is met will be triggered.
